WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:02.909
Hey, good morning family! Praise the Lord.

00:00:02.919 --> 00:00:06.670
It's day 58. I know we missed

00:00:06.680 --> 00:00:08.950
yesterday, but some things came up,

00:00:08.960 --> 00:00:11.589
so we're here today. I

00:00:11.599 --> 00:00:12.910
just want to thank you all for

00:00:12.920 --> 00:00:16.990
joining us. Diana has a word from the

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:20.509
Lord that I know is from the Lord.

00:00:20.519 --> 00:00:23.830
It's correction, but it's also beautiful.

00:00:23.840 --> 00:00:25.830
I love correction from the Lord

00:00:25.840 --> 00:00:27.790
because that's what makes us grow, and

00:00:27.800 --> 00:00:30.230
that's how we go from glory to glory.

00:00:30.240 --> 00:00:33.869
It's the Refiner's Fire

00:00:33.879 --> 00:00:36.830
that makes us stronger and

00:00:36.840 --> 00:00:39.830
causes us to be able to burn out

00:00:39.840 --> 00:00:41.910
all the

00:00:41.920 --> 00:00:46.549
junk, helping us to get deeper

00:00:46.549 --> 00:00:46.559
into

00:00:46.559 --> 00:00:48.630
those deeper wells, that deeper

00:00:48.640 --> 00:00:52.310
revelation of Him. I encourage

00:00:52.320 --> 00:00:54.349
you all to listen to what the Lord is

00:00:54.359 --> 00:00:57.990
saying here because it really

00:00:57.990 --> 00:00:58.000
is

00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:01.990
needed. I

00:01:02.000 --> 00:01:03.549
want her to get right to it and

00:01:03.559 --> 00:01:05.990
start reading what the Lord

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:08.870
said. I believe it will bless you,

00:01:08.880 --> 00:01:11.630
and we'll talk about it after.

00:01:11.640 --> 00:01:13.550
So, I was just going through my

00:01:13.560 --> 00:01:15.670
day and thinking about that

00:01:15.680 --> 00:01:18.630
saying that popped into my mind: 'Do

00:01:18.640 --> 00:01:21.550
what you need to do so that you can do

00:01:21.560 --> 00:01:24.670
what you want to

00:01:24.670 --> 00:01:24.680
do.'I

00:01:24.680 --> 00:01:26.870
was pondering that

00:01:26.870 --> 00:01:26.880
and

00:01:26.880 --> 00:01:28.109
thinking,

00:01:28.119 --> 00:01:31.550
'Wow, Lord, I need You.'You

00:01:31.550 --> 00:01:31.560
are

00:01:31.560 --> 00:01:33.749
also something I look

00:01:33.759 --> 00:01:36.830
forward to—my time with You.

00:01:36.840 --> 00:01:38.350
The first thing when I get up in the morning,

00:01:38.360 --> 00:01:40.670
I love spending time with Him,

00:01:40.680 --> 00:01:43.069
but as I'm going through my day,

00:01:43.079 --> 00:01:45.190
I'm looking forward to that

00:01:45.200 --> 00:01:47.230
as well. I was thinking, 'Wow God,

00:01:47.240 --> 00:01:49.469
I need You; You're on

00:01:49.479 --> 00:01:52.030
both sides of that.'During my

00:01:52.040 --> 00:01:54.190
prayer time later that evening,

00:01:54.200 --> 00:01:55.789
He started talking to me

00:01:55.799 --> 00:01:58.789
about that for the Body, or just in

00:01:58.799 --> 00:02:03.149
general. He said, 'The saying,

00:02:03.159 --> 00:02:05.310
"Do what you need to do so that you can

00:02:05.320 --> 00:02:07.910
do what you want to do"—I need to be on

00:02:07.920 --> 00:02:09.270
both sides of

00:02:09.280 --> 00:02:12.869
that. Fellowship with Me is something

00:02:12.879 --> 00:02:15.869
you need to do and should want to

00:02:15.869 --> 00:02:15.879
do.'Most

00:02:15.879 --> 00:02:19.309
people put Me on the want side or

00:02:19.319 --> 00:02:23.430
the need side, but rarely ever both. A

00:02:23.440 --> 00:02:26.110
heart that is right before Me will see

00:02:26.120 --> 00:02:29.470
Me as fitting in both categories, for I

00:02:29.480 --> 00:02:31.869
will not be neglected. If one

00:02:31.879 --> 00:02:34.470
fellowships with Me out of necessity so

00:02:34.480 --> 00:02:36.750
they can go watch a movie and live the

00:02:36.760 --> 00:02:39.830
rest of their day void of Me, they are

00:02:39.840 --> 00:02:42.030
missing it completely. It's like a

00:02:42.040 --> 00:02:43.790
time

00:02:43.790 --> 00:02:43.800
clock—clocking

00:02:43.800 --> 00:02:46.190
in and

00:02:46.200 --> 00:02:49.470
clocking out like for work or whatever.

00:02:49.480 --> 00:02:51.670
They will never see full

00:02:51.680 --> 00:02:54.110
manifestation of what they believe they

00:02:54.120 --> 00:02:57.790
have. Communion with Me, if they view

00:02:57.800 --> 00:03:00.509
relationship with Me as something

00:03:00.519 --> 00:03:03.390
they want to do, there will be

00:03:03.400 --> 00:03:05.589
many days where they will have

00:03:05.599 --> 00:03:08.149
so much they need to do. The enemy will

00:03:08.159 --> 00:03:10.949
keep them so busy that they will fall

00:03:10.959 --> 00:03:14.430
into bed and say a half prayer: 'I'm

00:03:14.440 --> 00:03:15.470
sorry

00:03:15.480 --> 00:03:18.830
Lord, I didn't have time for You

00:03:18.830 --> 00:03:18.840
today.'That

00:03:18.840 --> 00:03:21.630
is

00:03:21.640 --> 00:03:24.110
unacceptable. This

00:03:24.120 --> 00:03:27.430
is largely what happens in My Body. Give

00:03:27.440 --> 00:03:30.550
Me all, or you might as well be giving Me

00:03:30.560 --> 00:03:33.470
nothing, for I will not take your

00:03:33.480 --> 00:03:36.509
scraps. I am not the almighty God who

00:03:36.519 --> 00:03:37.789
waits for your

00:03:37.799 --> 00:03:41.390
leftovers. This is repulsive in My sight.

00:03:41.400 --> 00:03:45.350
This is not fellowship; this is duty. So

00:03:45.360 --> 00:03:47.710
if you want a God that does what is

00:03:47.720 --> 00:03:50.550
strictly necessary in your life, keep

00:03:50.560 --> 00:03:52.429
performing your duties.

00:03:52.439 --> 00:03:55.550
I love that—this is not fellowship,

00:03:55.560 --> 00:03:58.229
this is a duty. He's wanting

00:03:58.239 --> 00:04:00.229
fellowship.

00:04:00.239 --> 00:04:02.429
If you feel like

00:04:02.429 --> 00:04:02.439
you're

00:04:02.439 --> 00:04:04.390
put out because you have to talk to God

00:04:04.400 --> 00:04:06.309
today or have

00:04:06.309 --> 00:04:06.319
your

00:04:06.319 --> 00:04:08.350
relationship with the Lord,

00:04:09.920 --> 00:04:12.110
that's not

00:04:12.120 --> 00:04:14.869
fellowship.

00:04:14.879 --> 00:04:17.509
The way He said that, I

00:04:17.519 --> 00:04:21.270
went,

00:04:21.270 --> 00:04:21.280
'Oh.'I

00:04:21.280 --> 00:04:25.270
agree. If you want a

00:04:25.280 --> 00:04:27.830
God that does what is strictly necessary

00:04:27.840 --> 00:04:30.150
in your life, keep performing your

00:04:30.160 --> 00:04:32.110
duties as I will

00:04:32.120 --> 00:04:35.469
Mine. But if you want a life full of

00:04:35.479 --> 00:04:38.830
fellowship with Me, give Me your all. Give

00:04:38.840 --> 00:04:42.510
Me your everything. Let Me invade every

00:04:42.520 --> 00:04:45.110
part of your day, every part of your

00:04:45.120 --> 00:04:48.350
thoughts, every part of your being. They

00:04:48.360 --> 00:04:50.590
give Me the bare minimum but expect

00:04:50.600 --> 00:04:53.469
Me to give them the full maximum. They

00:04:53.479 --> 00:04:56.070
give Me so little but expect My hand to

00:04:56.080 --> 00:04:57.790
be open to them

00:04:57.790 --> 00:04:57.800
limitlessly.

00:04:57.800 --> 00:05:00.150
They make demands of

00:05:00.160 --> 00:05:02.390
Me that they have no business demanding

00:05:02.400 --> 00:05:05.670
and should be ashamed to ask of Me. For

00:05:05.680 --> 00:05:08.390
if they weren't here with Me on their

00:05:08.400 --> 00:05:10.830
good days, why should I be there for them

00:05:10.840 --> 00:05:12.150
on their bad

00:05:12.160 --> 00:05:16.150
days? What about Me? Such a selfish, bratty

00:05:16.160 --> 00:05:18.430
Body. They will perform their religious

00:05:18.440 --> 00:05:20.790
duty of putting in their time and dread

00:05:20.800 --> 00:05:24.150
it all day. 'I will get this out of

00:05:24.160 --> 00:05:26.350
the way,'they say. 'I will spend three

00:05:26.360 --> 00:05:28.830
hours with the Lord today,'and they do

00:05:28.840 --> 00:05:31.270
their duty so they can brag that

00:05:31.280 --> 00:05:33.710
they did and that they know My Word so

00:05:33.720 --> 00:05:36.870
well. Obviously, it didn't sink

00:05:36.880 --> 00:05:39.830
in. Then when something bad happens,

00:05:39.840 --> 00:05:42.230
they remind Me

00:05:42.240 --> 00:05:44.270
of it all the time—all the time they

00:05:44.280 --> 00:05:46.629
spent with Me. 'Well, I spent three hours

00:05:46.639 --> 00:05:48.150
with You yesterday, Lord; this shouldn't

00:05:48.160 --> 00:05:50.430
be happening to me.'They quote all

00:05:50.440 --> 00:05:52.189
their head knowledge,

00:05:52.199 --> 00:05:55.469
but it never sunk in. For if it

00:05:55.479 --> 00:05:57.510
did, they wouldn't be in this situation

00:05:57.520 --> 00:06:00.270
to begin with.

00:06:00.280 --> 00:06:02.029
Then He told me a story about a

00:06:02.039 --> 00:06:04.029
couple that gets married and has a child. It

00:06:04.039 --> 00:06:06.110
starts off well enough, but soon the wife

00:06:06.120 --> 00:06:08.830
grows bored and finds the husband dull.

00:06:08.840 --> 00:06:11.629
So she divorces

00:06:11.639 --> 00:06:14.710
him. He has limitless money, so it's not a

00:06:14.720 --> 00:06:17.150
problem for her. Her plan seems perfect.

00:06:17.160 --> 00:06:19.670
They have a child together, so she

00:06:19.680 --> 00:06:22.390
can have 18 years of child support

00:06:22.400 --> 00:06:24.390
while she goes out and

00:06:24.400 --> 00:06:26.670
parties.

00:06:26.680 --> 00:06:28.430
Through the years, she continues dropping

00:06:28.440 --> 00:06:30.629
the child off with Dad for a day or

00:06:30.639 --> 00:06:32.790
two, and when she comes back,

00:06:32.800 --> 00:06:34.870
she sticks out her hand and

00:06:34.880 --> 00:06:37.430
demands, 'I did my duty of letting

00:06:37.440 --> 00:06:39.469
the child spend the day with you, so give

00:06:39.479 --> 00:06:42.469
me my money.'It is given to

00:06:42.479 --> 00:06:44.710
her as she requested, and she leaves. All

00:06:44.720 --> 00:06:46.589
seems well until someone breaks into her

00:06:46.599 --> 00:06:48.830
house one night while she is alone.

00:06:48.840 --> 00:06:50.909
She calls screaming, 'Where are you, and

00:06:50.919 --> 00:06:53.029
why aren't you here protecting

00:06:53.029 --> 00:06:53.039
me?'You

00:06:53.039 --> 00:06:55.589
foolish woman. You got exactly what you

00:06:55.599 --> 00:06:58.029
wanted, but even you don't know what you

00:06:58.039 --> 00:07:00.629
want. How should the ex-husband be

00:07:00.639 --> 00:07:03.150
expected to know what you want? Even more,

00:07:03.160 --> 00:07:04.830
why should he even care

00:07:04.840 --> 00:07:06.710
what happens to you beyond the

00:07:06.720 --> 00:07:08.629
care of how it affects his child?

00:07:08.639 --> 00:07:11.309
Then you have people who have

00:07:11.319 --> 00:07:13.350
experiences with Me and use it as

00:07:13.360 --> 00:07:16.430
leverage against fellow believers. 'I hear

00:07:16.440 --> 00:07:18.869
God too, you know,'they say. 'He comes and

00:07:18.879 --> 00:07:21.990
visits me.'You foolish believer. Don't you

00:07:22.000 --> 00:07:23.830
know that all should experience

00:07:23.840 --> 00:07:26.230
fellowship with Me? Don't brag about

00:07:26.240 --> 00:07:29.110
getting the bare minimum passing grade. A

00:07:29.120 --> 00:07:31.390
student doesn't brag to another

00:07:31.400 --> 00:07:34.270
who got an A-plus: 'Hey, I got a passing grade

00:07:34.280 --> 00:07:36.869
too, you know. You're nothing special; we

00:07:36.879 --> 00:07:38.749
both graduate on the same

00:07:40.510 --> 00:07:40.520
day.'Such

00:07:43.479 --> 00:07:45.790
foolishness. Is it common practice to

00:07:45.800 --> 00:07:47.550
brag about doing the bare minimum

00:07:47.560 --> 00:07:49.589
to make one feel special? What

00:07:49.599 --> 00:07:55.469
tangled webs they weave. Woe to

00:07:55.479 --> 00:07:58.149
them. After hearing that

00:07:58.149 --> 00:07:58.159
a

00:07:58.159 --> 00:08:01.469
second time, I

00:08:01.479 --> 00:08:06.309
just

00:08:09.070 --> 00:08:09.080
thought,

00:08:11.080 --> 00:08:12.550
'Wow.'It's

00:08:15.440 --> 00:08:18.990
correction, and it

00:08:19.000 --> 00:08:21.909
challenges me because there

00:08:21.909 --> 00:08:21.919
are

00:08:21.919 --> 00:08:24.070
times I've done those

00:08:24.070 --> 00:08:24.080
things—being

00:08:24.080 --> 00:08:27.270
transparent, where

00:08:27.280 --> 00:08:29.029
you get into bed tired and say

00:08:29.029 --> 00:08:29.039
a

00:08:29.039 --> 00:08:30.510
halfway

00:08:30.510 --> 00:08:30.520
prayer:

00:08:30.520 --> 00:08:32.909
'I'm sorry, Lord,

00:08:32.919 --> 00:08:35.230
please

00:08:35.240 --> 00:08:36.949
forgive

00:08:40.149 --> 00:08:40.159
me.'Walking

00:08:41.120 --> 00:08:44.670
with Him

00:08:44.680 --> 00:08:45.470
in

00:08:45.480 --> 00:08:48.150
intimacy is

00:08:48.150 --> 00:08:48.160
a

00:08:48.160 --> 00:08:51.829
sacrifice for your flesh. Your

00:08:51.839 --> 00:08:53.310
flesh always thinks of things

00:08:53.310 --> 00:08:53.320
to

00:08:53.320 --> 00:08:55.470
do—cleaning

00:08:55.480 --> 00:08:57.910
the

00:08:57.920 --> 00:08:59.910
house

00:08:59.910 --> 00:08:59.920
or

00:08:59.920 --> 00:09:03.269
yard work. The devil will always

00:09:03.279 --> 00:09:06.269
come to distract

00:09:06.279 --> 00:09:09.269
you from intimacy with the Father.

00:09:09.279 --> 00:09:12.190
That's his main agenda:

00:09:12.200 --> 00:09:15.430
to bring strife

00:09:15.430 --> 00:09:15.440
and

00:09:15.440 --> 00:09:16.990
distract you from

00:09:17.000 --> 00:09:19.069
fellowship. When you're

00:09:19.079 --> 00:09:20.750
reading your Bible, you have a million

00:09:20.760 --> 00:09:22.430
other thoughts of

00:09:22.440 --> 00:09:23.750
what you should be doing,

00:09:23.760 --> 00:09:25.870
or when you're praying,

00:09:25.870 --> 00:09:25.880
you

00:09:28.310 --> 00:09:28.320
think

00:09:28.320 --> 00:09:30.670
about

00:09:30.680 --> 00:09:32.670
dishes

00:09:32.680 --> 00:09:35.870
in the sink. But you could be watching TV

00:09:35.870 --> 00:09:35.880
or

00:09:35.880 --> 00:09:38.470
flipping through YouTube

00:09:38.480 --> 00:09:40.750
and never have one of those thoughts

00:09:40.760 --> 00:09:42.750
because your flesh is being satisfied.

00:09:46.920 --> 00:09:48.829
As soon as you start

00:09:48.839 --> 00:09:50.269
reading your Bible, the devil

00:09:50.269 --> 00:09:50.279
says,

00:09:50.279 --> 00:09:52.509
'Hey, you should be

00:09:52.519 --> 00:09:54.389
pulling

00:09:54.399 --> 00:09:57.790
weeds.'It's

00:09:57.800 --> 00:10:00.710
amazing to me what he

00:10:00.720 --> 00:10:02.230
does in his

00:10:02.240 --> 00:10:04.790
tactics. When the

00:10:04.800 --> 00:10:08.069
Lord talked about

00:10:08.079 --> 00:10:11.750
leftovers, it made

00:10:11.760 --> 00:10:15.389
me sad. His whole

00:10:15.399 --> 00:10:18.990
desire, the reason He put you

00:10:19.000 --> 00:10:22.550
here, is to have intimacy with

00:10:22.550 --> 00:10:22.560
you.

00:10:22.560 --> 00:10:26.389
The whole reason

00:10:26.399 --> 00:10:30.230
His Son died was to

00:10:30.240 --> 00:10:34.269
get

00:10:34.279 --> 00:10:37.550
back what Adam and Eve lost in the

00:10:37.550 --> 00:10:37.560
Garden—the

00:10:37.560 --> 00:10:41.629
way they walked with Him

00:10:41.639 --> 00:10:45.389
every day.

00:10:52.399 --> 00:10:54.310
He brought His Son's

00:10:54.310 --> 00:10:54.320
sacrifice so

00:10:54.320 --> 00:10:56.790
He could

00:10:56.800 --> 00:10:59.829
dwell on the inside of you.

00:10:59.839 --> 00:11:03.310
He

00:11:05.600 --> 00:11:07.829
doesn't need an Ark of the Covenant

00:11:07.829 --> 00:11:07.839
or

00:11:07.839 --> 00:11:10.509
the holy of holies; He dwells

00:11:10.519 --> 00:11:12.110
inside

00:11:19.399 --> 00:11:21.389
each

00:11:21.399 --> 00:11:24.670
of us. Whenever He says

00:11:24.680 --> 00:11:27.470
this about the scraps and the story about the

00:11:37.560 --> 00:11:43.509
18 years of child

00:11:43.519 --> 00:11:46.790
support, He's saying He's not a 'child

00:11:46.790 --> 00:11:46.800
support'God.

00:11:46.800 --> 00:11:50.629
He wants the marriage

00:11:50.629 --> 00:11:50.639
and

00:11:50.639 --> 00:11:52.389
the

00:11:52.399 --> 00:11:55.550
relationship. He'll protect you, but

00:11:55.560 --> 00:11:57.750
if you're just after the money and

00:11:57.760 --> 00:12:00.430
what gets you barely

00:12:00.440 --> 00:12:02.430
into the Kingdom,

00:12:02.430 --> 00:12:02.440
He says,

00:12:02.440 --> 00:12:04.150
'You foolish woman, you don't even know

00:12:04.160 --> 00:12:06.870
what you want.'It's like

00:12:06.880 --> 00:12:08.710
seeking

00:12:08.720 --> 00:12:10.750
His hand versus

00:12:12.680 --> 00:12:15.829
seeking His face. if you

00:12:17.639 --> 00:12:20.470
lay on His

00:12:20.480 --> 00:12:22.310
chest and listen to His breath, He'll

00:12:22.320 --> 00:12:23.910
tell you the

00:12:23.920 --> 00:12:29.629
secrets, but it takes time.

00:12:29.639 --> 00:12:32.430
It's like

00:12:32.440 --> 00:12:34.430
a relationship with a

00:12:34.430 --> 00:12:34.440
spouse—it

00:12:34.440 --> 00:12:37.509
doesn't happen if you're

00:12:37.509 --> 00:12:37.519
just strangers.

00:12:37.519 --> 00:12:40.670
The

00:12:40.680 --> 00:12:42.509
more you talk,

00:12:42.519 --> 00:12:44.310
even if it's a cranky

00:12:44.320 --> 00:12:45.790
conversation after a bad

00:12:45.800 --> 00:12:48.629
day at work, you're building

00:12:48.629 --> 00:12:48.639
a

00:12:48.639 --> 00:12:51.389
relationship

00:12:56.480 --> 00:12:58.150
through

00:13:01.199 --> 00:13:04.389
dialogue.

00:13:05.639 --> 00:13:07.389
But if you

00:13:07.389 --> 00:13:07.399
say,

00:13:07.399 --> 00:13:08.790
'I'm going out

00:13:10.560 --> 00:13:11.910
to the club

00:13:13.240 --> 00:13:14.829
with my girlfriends;

00:13:19.199 --> 00:13:22.069
the TV dinner is in the freezer,

00:13:22.079 --> 00:13:23.949
and

00:13:23.959 --> 00:13:26.310
where's your

00:13:28.680 --> 00:13:30.470
wallet?'—that

